{
  "message": "\ud83d\udd27 Fix plugin structure and repository references\n\n## Changes\n\n### Repository References\n- Fixed all references from `ruvnet/claude-code-flow` to `ruvnet/claude-flow`\n- Updated 6 files in `.claude-plugin/`:\n  - plugin.json\n  - README.md\n  - docs/STRUCTURE.md\n  - docs/PLUGIN_SUMMARY.md\n  - docs/INSTALLATION.md\n  - docs/QUICKSTART.md\n\n### Added marketplace.json\n- Created `.claude-plugin/marketplace.json` with complete marketplace metadata\n- Includes plugin features, requirements, and MCP server configuration\n- Follows official Claude Code marketplace specification\n\n### Fixed hooks structure\n- Created `hooks/hooks.json` at root level (correct location per docs)\n- Implements 7 hook events:\n  - PreToolUse (Task, Write|Edit)\n  - PostToolUse (Task, Write|Edit, Bash)\n  - UserPromptSubmit\n  - SessionStart\n  - SessionEnd\n  - Notification\n  - SubagentStop\n- Integrates with claude-flow coordination system\n\n## Plugin Structure (Now Correct)\n```\nclaude-flow/\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 .claude-plugin/\n\u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 plugin.json          \u2713 Plugin metadata\n\u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 marketplace.json     \u2713 Marketplace distribution\n\u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 README.md            \u2713 Documentation\n\u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 docs/                \u2713 Additional docs\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 commands/                 \u2713 Slash commands (root)\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 agents/                   \u2713 Custom agents (root)\n\u2514\u2500\u2500 hooks/                    \u2713 Event handlers (root)\n    \u2514\u2500\u2500 hooks.json\n```\n\n\ud83e\udd16 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>",
